translated: Hommerberg, Lily Andersson-, dentist, Skövde, b. 7/6/06 in Höör, Malmöhus County, daughter of Carl Hommerberg and Jenny Broms. Married in 1936 to dentist Tage Andersson. Children: Thomas b. 1938, Mats b. 1944, Berit b. 1945. Lily graduated from Wallinska skolan in Stockholm in 1925 and obtained a degree in dentistry from Heidelberg in 1927. She also studied dentistry in Sweden the same year and became a licensed dentist in 1930. She worked as an assistant in Växjö in 1930 and as a district dentist in Tibro from 1930-1936 before starting her own practice and working as a school dentist in Tibro. She now has a practice in Skövde.
